Palm_Beach_Gardens.Juno Dunes Natural Area:
Juno Dunes Natural Area is a 576-acre (233 ha) nature preserve and park in Palm Beach County, Florida.


== Geography ==
The preserve is located at 14200 U.S. Highway 1, near the town of Juno Beach. The entrance to the west tract is located on the west side of U.S. Highway 1, 1/2 mile north of Donald Ross Road.
